  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Complete safewater project for 168 rural learners</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will complete a safe water project for  children at Mt Matedzi Secondary in  Manicaland District. The school  has an enrollment of 168 learners who battle for clean water in long queues at a community borehole . The project will set up pipes and taps in the school premises so that learners can safely access drinking water and water for the toilets . Children are currently missing out lessons as they spend time seeking water , this also affects their performance .</narrative>
  </description>
